        "sender_full_name": "Asei Inoue",
        "timestamp": 1734852201
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"621881\">Fady Adal</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/Syntax.20to.20parse.20binary.20strings/near/459551398\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Similarly, if I use the <code>num</code> syntax <code>∣00⟩</code> is understood as just <code>∣0⟩</code>. </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Is it?</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/OWv7gS7ZPV7w_NkOZ5SlSRfH/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/OWv7gS7ZPV7w_NkOZ5SlSRfH/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"814x358\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/OWv7gS7ZPV7w_NkOZ5SlSRfH/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><p>Give me a moment</p>",
        "id": 490367909,
        "sender_full_name": "Soundwave",
        "timestamp": 1734853421
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>cf.:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">elab</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">qubits</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"∣\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">num</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"⟩\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">term</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bits</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">raw</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getArg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getAtomVal</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">λ</span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↦</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">match</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">'</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"bp\">'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">false</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">'</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">true</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">false</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">-- You can handle this better but you get the idea</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Elab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Term</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">elabTerm</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Quote</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">quote</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">`term</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bits</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">none</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">test</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∣</span><span class=\"mi\">00</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">test</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 490368429,
        "sender_full_name": "Soundwave",
        "timestamp": 1734853960
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The lesson is perhaps that TSyntax needs lots of love to be immensely useful.</p>",
